{"tid":1697043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［領展公開嘅CCTV又有核彈 有疑似人腳出現］","createTime":"2019-11-06T14:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T02:05:22.000Z","uid":153864,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"014d5718cb3d552017911296fa71856156fd8528","tid":1697043,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4hooRCnaBu/?igshid=1n5exr393tfyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4hooRCnaBu%2F%3Figshid%3D1n5exr393tfyg&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=64403aa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4hooRCnaBu%2F%3Figshid%3D1n5exr393tfyg&h=aaf56d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4hooRCnaBu/?igshid=1n5exr393tfyg</a><br />\n<br />\n［領展公開嘅CCTV又有核彈？］<br />\n［請廣傳］<br />\nAdmin睇睇下CCTV<br />\n無啦啦發現係C30 2/F 01:02:24（見片2）<br />\n無啦啦喺閉路電視片段左上角出現咗一對疑似人腳（見圖1）<br />\n隨即畫面上嘅01:02:25個5字疑似出現跳格（見圖3-4上方時間）<br />\n最後對疑似人腳就消失左 （連殘影都冇喎）<br />\n我又發現咗疑似人腳出現嘅地方就係事發地點<br />\n（事發地點係NL1882嘅正後方）<br />\n（而疑似出現人腳嘅位置正下方 正正就係NL1882嘅後方）（見圖5-6）<br />\n唔係講笑 真係好奇怪<br />\n希望大家可以一齊分析一下<br />\n無可能咁巧合係案發地點無啦啦出現一對疑似人腳 仲要又咁啱跳格？？？<br />\nAdmin就個人認為片段被刪減<br />\n大家一定要廣傳出去！<br />\n如果唔係根本上冇可能知道真相."},{"pid":"fe9a3635b5ad921250a72bcfcd29dcb63a494767","tid":1697043,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"bec79418bcc3384f08c13a230ecab3e29cf47f22","tid":1697043,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"378c71d30bc6ddea683c5bdcf3bdd1dff2026c4f","tid":1697043,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"18ef764bb682057d3956998f83f62a09b8fe31f9","tid":1697043,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:54:13.000Z","